<l>oṉpā ṉiṟuti yurupunilai tiriyā</l>
<l>tiṉpeṟal vēṇṭuñ cāriyai moḻiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The final [part] of <foreign xml:lang="ta">oṉpāṉ</foreign> ' nine ' will not undergo any modification</l>
<l>[before words denoting measure and weight] ; it is necessary that</l>
<l>the empty word <foreign xml:lang="ta">iṉ</foreign> is added.<note place="foot">Eg. <foreign xml:lang="ta">oṉpatiṉkalam.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
